===== HOTKEYS in terminal ====================================================
ctrl k     cut line on right side of cursor
ctrl u     cut all line
ctrl y     paste
ctrl w     cut word

ctrl r     serach in history

ctrl l     clear


ctrl h
ctrl j


ctrl a      go to beginning line
ctrl e      go to end
alt b       go back 1 word
alt f       go forward 1 word























